column4: Y downloaded a game for a Page, that game open with flash player en WIndows XP, but I want it to open with the WINE on Ubuntu, but I can't Open it. It say "Exception EAccessViolation in module <name of the game.exe> at 005B29F0. Access violation at address 005B39F0. Write of address F70413A8. there's something I can do to open that file?
